
---

## 2. .gitignore 예시

`.gitignore` 파일을 프로젝트 폴더에 만들고 아래 내용을 넣으시면 됩니다.

```gitignore
# ============================================================
# Vivado generated files
# ============================================================

*.jou
*.log
*.str
*.zip
*.html
*.xml
*.pb
*.wdb
*.wcfg

# Vivado backup files
*.backup.*
*.bak
*~
.#*

# Vivado generated directories
.cache/
.hw/
.ip_user_files/
.sim/
.runs/
.gen/
.srcs/sources_1/bd/
.Xil/

# Simulation outputs
xsim.dir/
*.vcd
*.fst
*.saif

# Synthesis / implementation generated outputs
*.dcp
*.bit
*.ltx
*.mmi
*.rpt
*.rpx
*.edf
*.edn
*.ngc

# Vivado temporary files
usage_statistics_webtalk.html
usage_statistics_webtalk.xml
webtalk*.jou
webtalk*.log

# ============================================================
# OS / editor files
# ============================================================

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

.vscode/
.idea/

# ============================================================
# Keep important project files
# ============================================================

!*.xpr
!*.v
!*.sv
!*.vh
!*.xdc
!README.md
!.gitignore